        </item>
        <item>
            <title>ChatGPT 4o 图像生成「比预期受欢迎」，OpenAI 延迟开放予免费用户</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/27/gpt4o-image-generation/ai/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=gpt4o-image-generation</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/27/gpt4o-image-generation/ai/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 27 Mar 2025 09:00:32 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[人工智能]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[GPT-4o]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[openai]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1299668</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>OpenAI 最新推出的 GPT-4o 图像生成功能自亮相以来，因需求远超预期，OpenAI 宣布暂缓向免费用户开放此服务。行政总裁 Sam Altman 表示，这项功能在 ChatGPT 的受欢迎程度超出想像，目前仅限付费用户使用。该技术让用户可上传及修改图像，并以文字提示精准生成图片。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet"><p dir="ltr" lang="en">images in chatgpt are wayyyy more popular than we expected (and we had pretty high expectations).</p><p>rollout to our free tier is unfortunately going to be delayed for awhile.</p><p>— Sam Altman (@sama) <a href="https://twitter.com/sama/status/1905000759336620238?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">March 26, 2025</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>GPT-4o 图像生成技术于 3 月 25 日正式推出，允许用户透过文字指令生成或编辑图像，并能保持角色风格一致，应用范围涵盖设计、艺术创作等。据外媒报道，此功能推出后迅速掀起热潮，例如在 X 平台上，不少用户将日常场景或迷因转化为吉卜力动画风格，引发广泛讨论。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet"><p dir="ltr" lang="en">Today is a great internet day <a href="https://t.co/iPWl2yfvdq">pic.twitter.com/iPWl2yfvdq</a></p><p>— Zeneca.xyz 🔮 (@Zeneca) <a href="https://twitter.com/Zeneca/status/1904774204769411196?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">March 26, 2025</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>此技术有别于过往依赖 DALL-E 的图像生成方式，直接建基于 GPT-4o，强调精准度和上下文理解，所有生成图像均附 C2PA 元数据以标示 AI 来源。OpenAI 同时设限，禁止生成违规内容如 Deepfake 或不当图像。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet"><p dir="ltr" lang="ja">※ワンポチで漫画が描ける最强 AI</p><p>GPT-4oの画像生成なら、指定したキャラクターでも漫画が描けます！</p><p>絵心が壊灭な私でもこのクオリティ！ <a href="https://t.co/qAAgqAiaVY">https://t.co/qAAgqAiaVY</a><a href="https://t.co/DWBFrPIlVX">pic.twitter.com/DWBFrPIlVX</a></p><p>— 结パパ｜AIクリエイター (@Yuupapa_free) <a href="https://twitter.com/Yuupapa_free/status/1904702943095582802?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">March 26, 2025</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>OpenAI 近年屡因运算资源不足影响产品推展，例如去年 12 月 Sora 推出后曾暂停新用户注册。此次延迟亦被归咎于相同问题。为解决困境，公司正推进耗资 5,000 亿美元（约港币 3.8 万亿元）的 Stargate 数据中心计划，预计大幅提升 AI 运算能力。</p><p>GPT-4o 图像生成功能的热潮显示 AI 技术在创意领域的潜力，惟运算资源不足仍是 OpenAI 的挑战。随著 Stargate 计划推进，预计未来数月内免费用户有望体验此功能，而技术的持续优化或将进一步扩展其应用场景，值得关注。</p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://techcrunch.com/2025/03/26/chatgpts-new-ai-image-feature-is-delayed-for-free-users/">Tech Crunch</a></p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/27/gpt4o-image-generation/ai/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
            <slash:comments>0</slash:comments>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title>SNK《饿狼传说》加入足球巨星 C 朗，非仅宣传而是可操控角色、绝招用足球踢对手</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/27/c-ronaldo-joins-city-of-the-wolves/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=c-ronaldo-joins-city-of-the-wolves</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/27/c-ronaldo-joins-city-of-the-wolves/game-channel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 27 Mar 2025 08:05:43 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[游戏情报]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[SNK]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[饿狼传说]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1299654</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>日本老牌格斗游戏公司 SNK 宣布，足球巨星 Cristiano Ronaldo （C 朗）将登场《饿狼传说 City of the Wolves》。游戏预计于 4 月 24 日在 PlayStation 4、PlayStation 5、Xbox Series X/S 及 PC 平台推出。外界推测，这次跨界合作或与 C 朗效力沙地阿拉伯艾纳斯及 SNK 隶属沙地王储 MiSK 基金会有关。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299665" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032733455-694x373.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="373" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032733455-694x373.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032733455.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299661" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/fatalfury_cotwcr7ann-6-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/fatalfury_cotwcr7ann-6-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/fatalfury_cotwcr7ann-6.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299660" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/fatalfury_cotwcr7ann-5-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/fatalfury_cotwcr7ann-5-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/fatalfury_cotwcr7ann-5.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>SNK 这次将 C 朗引入《饿狼传说 City of the Wolves》，可谓一大创举。C 朗作为享誉全球的足球明星，曾效力多队顶尖球会，并在葡萄牙国家队担当核心角色。据网上分析，其加入游戏的契机与他自 2023 年起在沙地阿拉伯艾纳斯密切相关，而 SNK 现由沙国王储主导的 MiSK 基金会持有，两者关系促成这场别开生面的合作。官方介绍指，C 朗在游戏中以足球为基础设计招式，展现独特格斗风格，让玩家耳目一新。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299659" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/fatalfury_cotwcr7ann-4-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/fatalfury_cotwcr7ann-4-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/fatalfury_cotwcr7ann-4.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299658" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/fatalfury_cotwcr7ann-3-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/fatalfury_cotwcr7ann-3-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/fatalfury_cotwcr7ann-3.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299655" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/fatalfury_cotwcr7ann-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/fatalfury_cotwcr7ann-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/fatalfury_cotwcr7ann.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>《饿狼传说 City of the Wolves》是该系列睽违近 25 年的新作，除保留经典角色如不知火舞外，还加入《Street Fighter》的春丽和 Ken 等跨界角色。C 朗的实机战斗画面已于 3 月 27 日公开，展示他以足球结合武术的创新打法。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_32885"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/fbeEWm4_qeg?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>资料来源：<a href="https://www.inside.com.tw/article/37971-cristiano-ronaldo-fatal-fury-city-of-the-wolves-snk">Inside</a>、<a href="https://www.polygon.com/news/547300/cristiano-ronaldo-fatal-fury-city-of-the-wolves-snk">Polygon</a>、<a href="https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E7%9F%B3%E6%B2%B9%E7%8E%8B%E5%87%BA%E7%B5%95%E6%8B%9B%EF%BC%81%E3%80%8A%E9%A4%93%E7%8B%BC%E5%82%B3%E8%AA%AA-cow%E3%80%8B%E7%AB%9F%E6%8A%8A%E3%80%8Cc%E7%BE%85%E3%80%8D%E5%81%9A%E9%80%B2%E9%81%8A%E6%88%B2%EF%BC%8C%E9%A0%90%E5%91%8A%E5%85%AC%E9%96%8B%E7%94%A8%E8%B6%B3%E7%90%83%E6%94%BB%E6%93%8A-055245650.html">Yahoo</a></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2025/03/27/c-ronaldo-joins-city-of-the-wolves/game-channel/">SNK《饿狼传说》加入足球巨星 C 朗，非仅宣传而是可操控角色、绝招用足球踢对手</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
